      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, providing a reliable and comfortable driving experience. While there are some minor signs of normal wear and tear on the exterior and interior, it remains a solid and dependable choice for its next owner. All essential features are fully functional, and it is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34000.0,
