    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable companion that\u2019s ready for its next adventure! This vehicle is in honest, fair condition, showing some expected wear and tear from its years of service, but it remains a reliable choice for your daily needs. It\u2019s been well-loved and is perfect for someone who values functionality and character over a showroom finish. Drive away with confidence in a car that\u2019s built to keep going!",
