    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been preserved in an impeccable state, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the absolute precision of a new machine, having undergone an exhaustive technical validation to ensure it meets the most exacting standards of excellence. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly pristine, concours-level condition.",
      "price": 43500.0,
